news.title: Bombay HC seeks special fire-safety panel to give its recommendation by year end
news.para: A bench of chief justice Dipankar Datta and justice M S Karnik had on August 22 granted Singh the liberty to place her suggestions before the committee and directed that she be given a personal hearing too by the panel.

news.title: Repair of 12 Bowbazar buildings possible: Mayor
news.para: The 12 buildings that have developed cracks after the latest subsidence in Bowbazar last Friday may not have to be demolished. Initial survey carried out by structural engineers indicate that repairs can be carried out.

news.title: Hyderabad civic body announces 'one time scheme' for property tax arrears
news.para: ​GHMC said the state has announced a waiver of 90% accumulated arrears' interest on property tax, provided taxpayers clears the entire amount.
